description.en:
Horny doge aim is to create a game platform and nft platform.
Our Nft collection started to be published. 
The purpose of the Horny Doge project is to bring fun to those who support the project. Every day a new game is published on the telegram and the winner is awarded a prize. 
It is a nice project where chat and friendship meet. It was a good start to meet new friends. We love our family. We've been on the market for about a month now and have an ever-increasing volume of holders. 
One of our goals is to reduce the amount of tokens to the lowest level with the lowest automatic burn. 
5 Engineers have developed this project. 
The prize is distributed to 100 holders randomly in the first 500 wallets from the cut fee every week. 
We have a constantly updated website, project and holders that we are personally interested in. We act in accordance with the Roadmap.

Our first demo of NFTs:
